### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3333/api
@token = tu_token_aqui

### ============================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3333/

### ============================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN
### ============================================

### Registrar Usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@test.com",
  "contrasena": "12345678",
  "rol": "admin"
}

### Iniciar Sesión
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ruprecht.com",
  "contrasena": "12345678"
}

### Obtener Usuario Actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cerrar Sesión
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### PRODUCTOS
### ============================================

### Listar Todos los Productos
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### Listar Productos con Paginación y Filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=5&category=Electrónica

### Obtener Producto por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1

### Productos por Categoría
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/Electrónica

### Crear Producto (Requiere Auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto Nuevo",
  "description": "Descripción detallada del producto nuevo que estamos creando",
  "price": 199.99,
  "stock": 25,
  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e",
  "category": "Electrónica",
  "isActive": true
}

### Actualizar Producto (Requiere Auth)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Producto Actualizado",
  "price": 179.99,
  "stock": 30
}

### Activar/Desactivar Producto (Requiere Auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar Producto (Requiere Auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/11
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### CONTACTO
### ============================================

### Enviar Mensaje de Contacto (Público)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan@example.com",
  "subject": "Consulta sobre productos",
  "message": "Hola, me gustaría obtener más información sobre los productos disponibles. ¿Tienen envíos internacionales?"
}

### Listar Mensajes de Contacto (Requiere Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contact
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar Mensajes No Leídos (Requiere Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contact?is_read=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener Mensaje por ID (Requiere Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contact/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Marcar Mensaje como Leído (Requiere Auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contact/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar Mensaje (Requiere Auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contact/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
